InfoMonitor
===========

InfoMonitor is a derivative work based on LiteMonitor:
https://github.com/Diorser/LiteMonitor

The upstream project identifies Diorser as its author and declares the
project to be available under the MIT License in its README. The original
source code and its Git history retain their upstream authorship.

Modifications maintained by NikkicZh include, among other changes:

- Codex usage monitoring based on the local Codex sign-in state.
- Kimi usage monitoring based on the local Kimi Code CLI sign-in state.
- InfoMonitor repository branding and derivative-work documentation.

See LICENSE for the license text. Third-party dependencies and bundled
components remain subject to their respective licenses.
